<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469800>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Geographical distributions of trans-Andean species of Lasiancistrus individuals and species examined in this study. Key:purple stars, Lasiancistrus caucanus; orange triangles, Lasiancistrus guacharote; green circles, Lasiancistrus mayoloi; red diamonds, Lasiancistrus volcanensis; yellow squares, Lasiancistrus wiwa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469800/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469808>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Dorsal view of anterior portion of body.A, Lasiancistrus caucanus, CZUTIC12434, 98.83 mm standard length (SL). B, Lasiancistrus volcanensis, CZUTIC5898, 83.59 mm SL. C, Lasiancistrus mayoloi, CZUTIC21345, 91.68 mm SL.D, Lasiancistrus wiwa, CZUTIC17449, 79.55 mm SL. Abbreviations: F, frontal; PT, compound pterotic; SO, parieto-supraoccipital; SP, sphenotic. Scale bars:10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469810>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Ventral view of abdominal region.A, Lasiancistrus caucanus, CZUT-IC 12434, 98.83 mm standard length (SL). B, Lasiancistrus volcanensis, CZUT-IC 5898, 83.59 mm SL.C, Lasiancistrus mayoloi, CZUT-IC 21345, 91.68 mm SL. D, Lasiancistrus wiwa, CZUT-IC 17449, 79.55 mm SL. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469810/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469812>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Urohyal (UH) and hypohyals (HH) in ventral view. A, Lasiancistrus wiwa, CZUTIC17449, 79.55 mm standard length (SL). B, Lasiancistrus caucanus, CZUTIC12434, 98.83 mm SL. C, Lasiancistrus volcanensis, CZUTIC5898, 83.59 mm SL. D, Lasiancistrus mayoloi, CZUTIC21345, 91.68 mm SL. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469820>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Holotype of Lasiancistrus wiwa, CZUTIC17449, 79.6 mm standard length, from Colombia, Departamento de La Guajira, Ranchería River basin, Manantial Cañaverales. Scale bar: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

